messages.message:
:alarm: <!here> Looks like Prod Jenkins is choking on its own fumes somehow. Yields 502's when trying to auth, and not just it's usual "Oh your session is too weird, clear session cookies and try again" habit. :thonk:

Just a heads-up. Investigating now, will update here as things change

:yellow_circle: Prod Jenkins is back online and available, but I won't pretend to have done anything to effect its recovery, nor do I know what happened. :joy:

Looking further, will post again when I feel more confident in its stability
